	<blockquote>Looking to join The Hidden are you? The following steps must be taken to gain entrance
	to our halls.
	<ul>
		<li>You must be at least level 40(See below for Excepetions).</li>
		<li>You must send an email to all <a
		href="mailto:ug_mug@yahoo.com;charon86@hotmail.com?Subject=Application to The 
		Hidden">Officers</a> with the	following information: Why you want to join. Why you
		would be a good addition to The Hidden. Your Character(s) name, level, race, class,
		and usual playing time.	What previous guilds you have been in, why you left or why
		you want to leave for The Hidden. This application will be posted in the Members
		only section.</li>
		<li>Next a current member of The Hidden must sponsor you by starting a voting
		thread in the Members Only Voting Booth. A Member should only sponsor a Prospective
		member if they feel they would be a good addition to the guild. This means the
		sponsor should know the Prospective member and grouped with them before.</li>
		<li>All Members have one week from the time a Prospective is sponsored to vote.
		If two or more members vote no, your admission to The	Hidden is barred.
			<ul>
				<li>For those wishing to join below the level 40 minimum. You may be
				sponsored by a Member and if all votes are for you and the Council
				agrees you may join.</li>
			</ul>
		</li>
		<li>Once voting has taken place you shall be invited to the guild as soon as you
		can meet up with an officer.</li>
		<li>All twinks and secondary characters are welcome regardless of level.</li>
		<li>You will recieve the password to the Members Only section and are considered
		a full member, and as a member will follow the <a href="rules.asp">rules</a>
		governing members.</li>
	</ul>
	Best of luck to all prospective members.</blockquote>

